data.description: This 5 bedroom 4 bathroom newly renovated gem located in the highly sought after Hopyard Farm community is turn key! The entire interior has been freshly painted a neutral color that adds a clean, fresh touch and enhances any decor.  The main level has all new luxury flooring throughout from the foyer to the formal living and dining rooms all the way back to the powder room, large family room, office/playroom/flex space, gourmet kitchen, large walk-in pantry, and sunroom. There is a Trex and vinyl deck off the sunroom, offering even more entertaining possibilities and a great view of the backyard. Upstairs you'll find new carpet on the steps, new luxury flooring on the landing, and new flooring in the hallway and large linen closet as well. The more than generously sized primary bedroom located at the top of the steps and on the back of the home has two great size closets, an updated primary bathroom with a stall shower and a soaking tub, perfect to relax in after a long day.  The laundry room, a large linen closet, hallway bathroom and four additional bedrooms, one with an attached bathroom, are also located upstairs. All of these rooms also have new ceiling fans too, as well as fresh paint! The basement has a huge finished rec space, a full finished bathroom, unfinished storage spaces, and walk-up access to the backyard. The two car garage is front load and has remote door opener. All of this and more all located in an amenity-filled community with community clubhouse with fitness center/party room/game room and office center, gorgeous in-ground pool, tennis courts, playgrounds, walking trails, boat ramp access and more! Conveniently located within commuting distance to Richmond, Southern Maryland, Fredericksburg, and Quantico! You don't want to miss this gorgeous and spacious gem of a home!
